modName: Ethereal Elven Overhaul-The Way of the Dovahkiin - Ultimate Deadly Encounters aka Sands of Time Compatibility Patch
summary: Patch that makes EEO fully compatible with The Way of the Dovahkiin - Ultimate Deadly Encounters aka Sands of Time
descriptionHtml:
This is a very simple esp that ensures the NPCs that EEO makes changes to receive the tags from The Way of the Dovahkiin - Ultimate Deadly Encounters aka Sands of Time. 

Previously if one used both mods all of the elves that were supposed to have innocent tags would lose them due to the changes EEO makes; now should the player choose to kill the innocent elves there will be repercussions. Judgement !!

You must have both mods

The Way of the Dovahkiin - Ultimate Deadly Encounters aka Sands of Time                                          http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/12452

Ethereal Elven Overhaul
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24273

Please endorse if you have not done so already, all credit goes to Tony and Nuska
author: Disciple Darkfriend
